subject: Basketball (College)
NCAA Basketball Championships (Women)
lead_paragraph: North Carolina, a No. 4 seed, was down by 18 points in the second half before coming back to defeat 13th-seeded Tennessee-Martin, 60-58, in the first round of the N.C.A.A. tournament.
